1. sdl2 port:
    * online TV/monitor display mode switching
    * performance rendering / tests resize + hide by other windows on both machines
    * character programming flicker is almost gone -> frame frquency 25Hz (closer to PAL anyway)

2. features:
    * gui either homebrew or sdl2_image/guisan
        * CPU status / debug / disassembler / frequency control
        * Sound VU / disable single sound channels
    * snapshot: save whole machine state
    * recorder: snapshot + track user interactions with cpu (or frame) timestamp

